results.name: Air Jordan 12 Retro PS 'Arctic Pink'
results.story: Built for little kids, the Air Jordan 12 Retro PS ‘Arctic Pink’ delivers a refreshed take on the classic silhouette that Michael Jordan wore when he captured his fifth NBA title. In addition to the non-traditional palette, the stitched upper is treated to a distressed finish, featuring textured pink remnants that create an abstract pattern on a light grey backdrop. A more intense shade of pink lands on the sneaker’s collar lining, pull tab and branding elements, which include an embroidered Jumpman atop the tongue.

results.name: Air Max 2090 SE GS 'Dark Purple Dust'
Flex Runner PS 'Crimson Bliss Metallic Platinum'
results.story: Constructed for little kids, the Nike Flex Runner PS ‘Crimson Bliss Metallic Platinum’ delivers a versatile silhouette that can be slipped easily on and off, thanks to a laceless mesh upper with webbing pull tabs at the tongue and heel. The sneaker’s warm coral hue is offset by a metallic silver Swoosh that adorns a supportive midfoot cage. The lightweight build is supported by a cushy foam sole unit, featuring flex grooves underfoot that promote a smooth, natural stride.

results.name: Adizero Spark MD J 'Royal Blue'
results.story: The adidas Adizero Spark MD J ‘Royal Blue’ delivers a lightweight two-tone football cleat built for little kids. The streamlined upper is constructed from coated Sprintskin, emblazoned with three-stripe branding on the lateral toe. Breathable mesh is utilized on the padded collar and tongue. A low-profile Bounce midsole is supported by a molded Quickframe outsole, featuring an aggressive lug pattern for stop-and-go traction.

results.name: Superstar J 'Pink Iridescent'
results.story: Built for little kids, the adidas Superstar J ‘Pink Iridescent’ updates the shell-toed sneaker icon with an eye-catching finish. The pink leather upper is accented with serrated white leather three-stripes and multicolor iridescent paneling on the sneaker’s lateral side. A similar iridescent finish is applied to adidas branding hits on the tongue and heel tab. The low-top is mounted on a durable rubber cupsole, complete with a herringbone traction pattern underfoot.

results.name: Swift Run X J 'Black Fluorescent Pop'
results.story: Built for little kids, the adidas Swift Run X J ‘Black Fluorescent Pop’ treats the retro-inspired low-top to an essential black and white color scheme, enlivened with fluorescent pops of color on the eyelets and forefoot. An Ortholite sockliner combines with an EVA midsole to deliver soft cushioning with each step. Underfoot, a black rubber outsole is equipped with a series of flex grooves that accommodate the natural motion of the foot.

results.name: Revolution 5 SE PS 'Crimson Tint Multi'
results.story: The Nike Revolution 5 SE PS ‘Crimson Tint Multi’ highlights a pastel finish on a versatile sneaker designed for little kids. Elastic no-tie laces combine with a webbing pull tab and an adjustable hook-and-loop strap to provide easy on and off. The upper, constructed from peach-colored knit textile and accented with a color-fade Swoosh, rides on a plush foam midsole. Underfoot, a full-length rubber outsole in Glacier Blue offers durable traction.

results.name: MD Valiant GS 'White Multi'
results.story: Crafted for big kids, the Nike MD Valiant GS ‘White Multi’ highlights a limited spectrum of pastel accents on a casual sneaker inspired by ‘80s running style. The upper is constructed from white textile with tonal synthetic leather overlays at the toe and heel. The signature Swoosh is rendered in a gradient blend of yellow, blue and pink hues, a color combination that’s repeated on the Nike logo that adorns the iridescent heel tab. A waffle-traction rubber outsole delivers an additional nod to Nike heritage.

results.name: Lite Racer Adapt 4.0 J 'Grey Super Pop'
results.story: The adidas Lite Racer Adapt 4.0 J ‘Grey Super Pop’ makes use of a grey open-mesh upper with laceless slip-on construction, allowing little kids to easily slip on and off their shoes. Bright pink accents land on a webbing pull tab and an elastic midfoot strap marked with adidas branding. A second adidas wordmark is debossed on a stitched TPU heel patch. The casual sneaker rides on a plush Cloudfoam sole unit, good for lightweight cushioning with every step.

results.name: Lite Racer Adapt 4.0 J 'Black Solar Red'
results.story: Built for little kids, the adidas Lite Racer Adapt 4.0 J ‘Black Solar Red’ features convenient slip-on construction on a lightweight silhouette inspired by classic running shoes. Breathable black mesh is utilized on the upper, secured with an elastic midfoot strap marked with adidas branding in oversized orange lettering. The minimalist upper rests on a plush Cloudfoam sole unit in a contrasting white finish. Underfoot, a modified waffle tread delivers reliable grip.

results.name: Roma Basic Summer Jr 'Castlerock'
results.story: The PUMA Roma Basic Summer Jr ‘Castlerock’ dresses the retro low-top in a grey nylon upper with tonal leather overlays at the toe and heel. Traditional branding elements include a white leather Formstrip and ‘PUMA Roma’ stamped in gold lettering on the lateral quarter panel. An unexpected pop of yellow wraps around a full-length foam midsole, supported by a gum rubber outsole that wraps up the toe for added durability and grip.

results.name: Roma Basic Summer Jr 'Pink Lady Poppy Red'
results.story: The PUMA Roma Basic Summer Jr ‘Pink Lady Poppy Red’ features eye-catching hues on a vintage silhouette originally made to celebrate Italy’s victory at the 1968 Euro Cup in Rome. A bold pink finish saturates the lightweight textile upper, fortified with tonal leather overlays and accented with a bright red Formstrip. A two-tone foam midsole delivers a smooth ride. Underfoot, a durable gum rubber outsole features an exaggerated herringbone tread for optimal grip.

results.name: Roma Basic Summer Jr 'Black Star Sapphire'
results.story: Made for little kids, the PUMA Roma Basic Summer Jr ‘Black Star Sapphire’ updates the retro low-top with sharply contrasting accents in primary colors. The upper is constructed from black textile with tonal synthetic nubuck overlays at the toe and heel. The one-note finish is disrupted by gold-foil PUMA Roma branding and a stitched blue leather Formstrip. A two-tone foam midsole delivers a cushy ride, while a gum rubber outsole provides non-slip traction.

results.name: Suede Classic Jr 'Mono Iced - Aruba Blue'
results.story: Crafted for big kids, the PUMA Suede Classic Mono Iced JR ‘Aruba Blue’ features a monochromatic pastel finish on a vintage silhouette originally released in 1968. The low-top’s eponymous upper is accented with tonal branding elements, including a stitched Formstrip, ‘PUMA Suede’ debossed on the lateral quarter panel, and a jumping cat logo on the heel tab. The aqueous coloring up top continues on the iced-out translucent rubber cupsole.

results.name: Suede Teams Jr 'Los Angeles Lakers'
results.story: The PUMA Suede Teams Jr ‘Los Angeles Lakers’ celebrates one of the NBA’s winningest franchises with a soft suede upper draped in purple and gold. ‘PUMA Suede’ is etched in metallic gold lettering on the sneaker’s lateral side, matching a jumping cat logo stamped on each heel tab. A skyline graphic on the mesh sockliner pays further tribute to the City of Angels. The low-top is mounted on a durable rubber cupsole in a pristine white finish.

results.name: RS-X3 Twill Jr 'Castlerock Poppy Red'
results.story: Built for big kids, the PUMA RS-X3 Twill Jr ‘Castlerock Poppy Red’ reinterprets classic RS style through a maximalist lens. Dark grey open mesh is utilized on the upper, accented with contrasting red no-sew overlays and a crisp white PUMA Formstrip marked with visible zigzag stitching. The bulky silhouette is accentuated with a stacked compression-molded EVA midsole, featuring geometric TPU pieces affixed to the raised sidewalls.

results.name: RS-X Jr 'Mothman'
results.story: Crafted for big kids, the PUMA RS-X Jr ‘Mothman’ draws inspiration from the world of cryptozoology. The lifestyle runner makes use of a textile and suede upper finished in muted earth tones with cracked, distressed finishes and wing-inspired graphics. The signature PUMA Formstrip is rendered in a deconstructed puff print, while the webbing pull tab that loops over the tongue mimics the look of evidence tape. ‘Mothman’ is inscribed on the custom sockliner, a nod to the cryptid that purportedly stalks the hills of West Virginia.

results.name: LeBron 18 PS 'Soundwave'
results.story: Built for little kids, the Nike LeBron 18 PS ‘Soundwave’ delivers a music-themed take on LeBron James’ signature shoe. Mismatched color blocking distinguishes the pair, featuring neon Volt accents on the left shoe and Bright Crimson on the right. Both shoes carry a black textile knit upper with matching black foam midsoles. Atop the tongue, a playful graphic depicts a cartoon lion wearing a crown and headphones. A volume dial graphic adorns the custom sockliner.

results.name: RS-X3 Twill Jr 'White Peacoat'
results.story: The PUMA RS-X3 Twill Jr ‘White Peacoat’ combines airy mesh construction with a compression-molded EVA midsole, packed with lightweight foam for extra-soft cushioning. Geometric TPU pieces affixed to the sidewalls complement the dynamic lines that distinguish the upper. Navy suede overlays are accompanied by yellow no-sew skins and a white leather Formstrip outlined with exposed zigzag stitching. A plush tongue and padded mesh collar enhance the sneaker’s comfortable fit.

results.name: RS-X3 Twill Jr 'Grey Violet Pink'
results.story: Offered in grade school sizing, the PUMA RS-X3 Twill Jr ‘Grey Violet Pink’ showcases pastel accents on a lifestyle runner that marries bold styling with cushioned comfort. The sneaker’s grey mesh upper is reinforced with tonal suede overlays and contrasting pink no-sew skins. Exposed zigzag stitching in the same pink hue traces the curved topline of the PUMA Formstrip. Lavender pops of color land on the padded collar and tongue. A bulky compression-molded EVA midsole features exaggerated sidewalls fitted with angular TPU pieces.

results.name: Air Jordan 3 Retro PS 'Georgetown'
results.story: Crafted for little kids, the Air Jordan 3 Retro PS ‘Georgetown’ features the signature colors of the Hoyas, the first in a long line of competitors felled by Michael Jordan with the final shot in a title game. The upper is built with navy tumbled leather, accented with grey elephant-print overlays at the toe and heel. Both the sneaker’s tongue and molded heel tab are trimmed with iconic Jumpman branding. A foam midsole delivers a cushioned ride, absent the visible Air sole unit of the mainline release.

results.name: Suede Teams Jr 'Knicks'
results.story: Made for big kids, the PUMA Suede Teams Jr ‘Knicks’ wears an upper dressed in the signature colors of New York City’s NBA franchise. The low-top’s suede build combines a royal blue base with contrasting orange hits on the Formstrip, tongue tag and collar lining. Metallic gold branding elements include ‘PUMA Suede’ stamped on the lateral quarter panel and the brand’s jumping cat logo on the heel tab. The rich hues up top are countered by a rubber cupsole in a stark white finish.

results.name: Suede Classic Jr 'Mono Iced - Sun Kissed Coral'
results.story: The PUMA Suede Classic Mono Iced Jr ‘Sun Kissed Coral' updates the iconic silhouette with a vibrant one-note finish throughout the sneaker’s exterior. The soft suede upper is accented with a stitched Formstrip and ‘PUMA Suede’ debossed on the lateral quarter panel. Perforated detailing offers improved breathability, while a padded low-cut collar delivers a comfortable fit. The minimalist build is anchored by a translucent rubber cupsole.

results.name: Roma Basic Summer Little Kid 'Black Star Sapphire'
Kyrie 7 GS 'Hip-Hop'
results.story: Made for big kids, the Nike Kyrie 7 GS ‘Hip-Hop’ honors the influential role that Brooklyn played in the history of rap culture. The homage is cemented with a boom box graphic embroidered on the heel, while the white and black color scheme gives the nod to the hometown Nets. The mid-top rides on a resilient foam midsole, accented with a contrasting pop of mint green on the lateral forefoot. 360-degree traction arrives via a computer-generated rubber outsole.

results.name: Roma Basic Summer Little Kid 'Pink Lady Poppy Red'
Zoom Freak 2 PS 'Denim'
results.story: Constructed for little kids, the Nike Zoom Freak 2 PS ‘Denim’ outfits Giannis Antetokounmpo’s second signature shoe with a grey textile upper. In addition to an oversized black Swoosh on the lateral side panel, the left and right shoe are enlivened with mismatched branding elements in aqua and Bright Mango accents. The low-top sits on a full-length foam midsole, dusted with speckled detailing and reinforced by a decouple rubber outsole.

results.name: Zoom Freak 2 GS 'Denim'
results.story: Built for big kids, the Nike Zoom Freak 2 GS ‘Denim’ dresses Giannis Antetokounmpo’s second signature shoe with a grey textile upper, overlaid with white synthetic leather on the medial side and accented with mismatched aqua and Bright Mango accents. The low-top rides on a speckled foam midsole, bolstered with a molded TPU piece on the lateral sidewall for added containment and stability. Underfoot, a decoupled rubber outsole provides flexible traction.

results.name: Terrex Trailmaker J 'White Teal'
results.story: Crafted for little kids, the adidas Terrex Trailmaker J ‘White Teal’ highlights candy-bright hues on a rugged trail shoe designed for outdoor adventures. Breathable white mesh is utilized on the upper, secured with an adjustable strap and rope laces integrated into the midfoot cage. A welded TPU mudguard wraps around the forefoot for added durability. Neon yellow coloring stands out on the full-length EVA midsole, supported underfoot by a lugged Traxion outsole made with grippy Continental rubber.

Air Max 2090 GS 'Topography'
results.story: Built for big kids, the Nike Air Max 2090 GS ‘Topography’ presents a simplistic two-tone colorway of the lifestyle runner that takes its cues from the classic Air Max 90 silhouette. Carried over from the older shoe are a cropped Swoosh, molded heel patch and leather mudguard, embellished with multiple Swooshes and wavy lines that mimic the look of a topographic map. The sneaker rides on a soft foam midsole, its solid black sidewalls offset by a red-tinged Max Air unit under the heel.

results.name: Kyrie 7 GS 'Chinese New Year'
results.story: The Nike Kyrie 7 GS ‘Chinese New Year’ delivers a celebratory colorway of Kyrie Irving’s seventh signature shoe made for big kids. In a nod to the lunar holiday, the sneaker’s heel overlay is accented with a red Chinese knot, superimposed with an embroidered gold Swoosh. A larger knotted gold Swoosh adorns the lateral side of the upper, built with pink and blue mesh. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a Phylon midsole, its sidewalls wrapped up by a data-inspired rubber outsole.

results.name: Air Jordan 1 Mid PS 'Purple Pulse Glacier Blue'
Kaptir 2.0 J 'Core Black'
results.story: Built for little kids, the adidas Kaptir 2.0 J ‘Core Black’ delivers a monochromatic colorway of a running-inspired sneaker intended for everyday wear. A speed lacing system secures the breathable knit upper, featuring seamless construction for a sock-like fit. A synthetic leather heel counter provides added support and durability, while a mesh-lined interior offers step-in comfort. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a sculpted Cloudfoam sole in contrasting white finish.

results.name: Kyrie 7 GS 'Play for the Future'
results.story: Constructed for big kids, the Nike Kyrie 7 ‘Play for the Future’ takes inspiration from Kyrie Irving’s commitment to a sustainable lifestyle, including his vegan diet. In addition to a plant-based color scheme, the heel overlay is embroidered with a sprouted KI logo. Laces are looped into molded forefoot fins for a lockdown fit, while the midsole packs soft foam in the forefoot for plush cushioning and firmer foam in the heel for improved stability. A bright turquoise outsole wraps up the sidewalls for maximum grip.

results.name: Blazer Low '77 PS 'White Midnight Navy'
results.story: Crafted for little kids, the Nike Blazer Low ‘77 PS ‘White Midnight Navy’ steps out in an elemental two-tone colorway. The white leather upper is reinforced with tonal suede overlays and secured with traditional laces and an added hook-and-loop strap that wraps over the midfoot. Contrasting navy hits land on the sneaker’s branding elements, including the signature retro Swoosh and a Nike wordmark on the heel tab. Underfoot, a herringbone gum rubber outsole provides grippy traction.

results.name: Dame 7 J 'Rose City'
results.story: Built for little kids, the adidas Dame 7 J ‘Rose City’ pays tribute to Portland, Oregon, Damian Lillard’s adopted hometown. An all-over graphic print made up of pink roses enlivens the breathable mesh upper, secured with an integrated lacing system and fortified with a black synthetic nubuck heel. Dame’s personal logo adorns the mesh tongue, while adidas’ signature three-stripes lands on the nubuck eyestay. Responsive cushioning arrives via a full-length Lightstrike midsole.

LEGO x FortaRun Little Kid 'Dots - White'
results.story: Launching as part of a larger collection with the Danish toymaker, the LEGO Dots x adidas FortaRun Little Kid ‘White’ features a seamless textile upper, accented with purple three-stripes and a multicolor monogram-like print. A webbing pull tab at the heel combines with elastic laces and an adjustable ankle strap to provide easy on and off for growing feet. The lightweight sneaker is supported by a full-length foam midsole that offers plush cushioning and a smooth ride.

results.name: LEGO x FortaRun Big Kid 'Dots - White'
LEGO x Sport Big Kid 'Shock Blue'
results.story: Taken from an apparel and footwear collection developed with the iconic toy brand, the LEGO x adidas Sport Big Kid ‘Shock Blue’ provides cushioned comfort for growing feet. An embossed texture on the molded heel tab and rubber outsole draw direct inspiration from LEGO bricks, as does the shoe’s bold color palette. The lightweight mesh and textile build, composed of 50% recycled content and zero virgin polyester, sits on a full-length foam midsole with partially wrapped sidewalls for enhanced durability.

results.name: LEGO x Sport Big Kid 'Bright Cyan'
LEGO Ninjago x FortaRun X J 'Lloyd'
results.story: Releasing as part of a collaborative series with the iconic toy brand, the LEGO Ninjago x adidas FortaRun X J ‘Lloyd’ delivers a versatile sneaker built for little kids. The dark emerald textile upper is accented with black three-stripes and kinetic graphics around the forefoot. A Ninjago wordmark is inscribed on a webbing pull tab at the heel, which combines with elastic laces and an adjustable ankle strap to allow the shoe to be slipped easily on or off. A plush foam midsole delivers lightweight cushioning.

results.name: LEGO x FortaRun Little Kid 'Dots - Black'
results.story: The LEGO Dots x adidas FortaRun Little Kid ‘Black’ is drawn from a larger collection created in partnership with the Danish toymaker. Multicolor Dots branding enlivens a one-piece textile upper, secured with elastic laces and an adjustable strap that wraps over the ankle. A webbing pull tab affixed to the heel facilitates easy on and off. The minimalist sneaker is mounted on a full-length foam midsole that offers lightweight cushioning with every step.

results.name: NMD_R1 V2 J 'Solar Yellow'
results.story: Built for big kids, the adidas NMD_R1 V2 J ‘Solar Yellow’ showcases an eye-catching palette designed to make a statement. A fluorescent yellow color suffuses all components of the shoe, spanning the one-piece knit upper, responsive Boost midsole and durable rubber outsole. A molded lace jewel depicts a cloud-like adidas Trefoil, an image that’s repeated on the tongue tag and heel. Those playful branding elements are joined by a bold adidas wordmark on the heel strap and forefoot EVA plug.

results.name: LEGO x Sport Little Kid 'Shock Blue'
LEGO Ninjago x FortaRun X J 'Kai'
results.story: The LEGO Ninjago x adidas FortaRun X J ‘Kai’ is taken from an apparel and footwear collection designed in partnership with the Danish toy brand. Varying crimson hues are applied to the textile upper, embellished with tonal three-stripes and a unique flame graphic across the toe. Elastic laces and an adjustable hook-and-loop ankle strap combine to deliver a secure fit. Ninjago branding adorns a webbing pull tab at the heel, rendered in a contrasting black finish and good for easy on and off.
